<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="complaint-n">complaint <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kəm'pleɪnt/    美 /kəm'pleɪnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 抱怨；不满；投诉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>letter of complaint</strong>
投诉信</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have no <strong>complaint about</strong> my pay. 
关于薪水我没有什么不满。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why don’t you <strong>make a complaint against</strong> your noisy neighbours? 
你为什么不投诉吵闹的邻居呢？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In time of difficulty, what we need is not <strong>complaint to</strong> each other but understanding of each other. 
困难的时候，我们需要的不是相互抱怨而是互相理解。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 抱怨 / 投诉的事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have a number of complaints about the hotel room you’ve given me. 
我对你给我的旅馆房间有许多不满。</p></div></div>